{"tid":2455704,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"法國籍「炸彈獵人」大潭發現5枚戰時炸彈","createTime":"2021-03-21T10:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T12:02:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"36cc1e8fe3b519efc67cd4ca1b382d3139d64e34","tid":2455704,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:31:26.000Z","msg":"中午12時50分，經常發現戰時炸彈的法國籍「炸彈獵人」報案，指在赤柱大潭郊野公園範圍內，發現多枚戰時手榴彈及彈殼等。警方接報到場，封鎖範圍，並召來爆炸品處理課（EOD）到場處理。拆彈專家帶同軍用金屬探測器到場，初步發現有4枚手榴彈及一枚未確定性質的炸彈。現場是衞奕信徑第一段，距離赤柱峽道約50米；警方正封鎖上山入口。<br />\n<br />\n發現手榴彈的Edward（28歲）法國人，是一位軍事迷，來港約7年，從事紅酒生意，平日會攜同金屬探測器，在本港不同地方尋找戰時遺下的軍火，包括二戰時期的英式迫擊炮彈及多款手榴彈。不過警方曾表示，手榴彈一旦爆炸，威力難以預測，呼籲行人人士不要帶同金屬探測器在山頭尋找戰時炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210321/GGROWZH2HNEEVO6544LNLVT2EI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210321%2FGGROWZH2HNEEVO6544LNLVT2EI%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfTIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=89de0a33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210321%2FGGROWZH2HNEEVO6544LNLVT2EI%2F&h=4e0807ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210321/GGROWZH2HNEEVO6544LNLVT2EI/</a>"},{"pid":"6e3c29ecdde2664521e4f82c8c88e1e6658e5e20","tid":2455704,"uid":17443,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.konami.com/games/bomberman/r/s/img/chara_shiro.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.konami.com%2Fgames%2Fbomberman%2Fr%2Fs%2Fimg%2Fchara_shiro.png&h=56ad7530&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad5a021500b1491281a5ad9e263d6e86d845363b","tid":2455704,"uid":315329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e3c29ecdde2664521e4f82c8c88e1e6658e5e20","tid":2455704,"uid":17443,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.konami.com/games/bomberman/r/s/img/chara_shiro.png\" data-th